text: Stephen Turner (born 17 September 1964) is a British rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:British male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Great Britain Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Barnstaple
